				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				1. Where do you buy the silver? From the jewler?<BR>
Silver and gems are both bought from a jewler<BR>
<BR>
2. Can I assume there is only 1 type of jeweler's kit unlike the sewing kit that comes in 2 sizes? If there are different kits, what are there uses?<BR>
There is as far as i know only 1 kit<BR>
<BR>
3. Where do you place the siver and where do you place the stone?<BR>
The silver and the stone are both placed in the kit which is bought from a jewler, the postion does not matter<BR>
<BR>
4. Do you have to have a stone?<BR>
Yes a stone is needed<BR>
<BR>
5. If the stone affects the jewelry, how does it?<BR>
The stone affects the magic properties of the jewlery and the type made (i.e ring, necklace)<BR>
6. Can you control the type of jewelry crafted?<BR>
Only by changing the stone<BR>
7. What are the hallmark skill levels/threshold for making jewelry.<BR>
This can be found in a jewlery guide
